name: EDEN
public_notice: ARCH is currently undergoing migration to EDEN. For more information, visit https://medium.com/archer-dao/arch-token-migration-915e6af976c6.

description.en: Eden is a priority transaction network that protects traders from frontrunning, aligns incentives for block producers, and redistributes miner extractable value.
